@startuml
title BP-22 - Parent Selects Bills and Creates Checkout

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Parent Guardian|
start
:View outstanding bills;
:Select one or more obligations to pay;
:Choose payment method;
:Submit checkout request;

|Platform|
:Validate selected obligations belong to same tenant;
:Validate selected obligations belong to same student for current MVP;
:Validate parent or student access;
:Calculate total amount server side;
:Validate payment amount does not exceed outstanding;

if (Validation passed?) then (Yes)
  :Create PaymentOrder with status PENDING;
else (No)
  :Return checkout validation error;
  stop
endif

|Parent Guardian|
:Receive payment order details;
stop

note right
Current MVP endpoint:
POST /payment-orders
Current model uses PaymentOrder rather than separate Checkout entity.
end note
@enduml
